!!! Japanese Keyboard with Key Overlay winnage
!!!
!!! Thanks to the At Home Modifier (https://gitorious.org/at-home-modifier) for
!!! such a great hack :)

! Caps Lock (overlaid with Control_L)
clear  Lock
keycode  66 = Escape

! Henkan (overlaid with Control_R)
keycode 100 = BackSpace

! Muhenkan (overlaid with Control_L)
keycode 102 = Tab

! Hiragana-Katakana (overlaid with Alt_R)
keycode 101 = Return

! Make colon easier to press
keycode  47 = colon semicolon colon semicolon
